Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, the judgment on Ochoko-Matsumoto will come tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.62,0:00:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier, I introduced him to a gastropub owned by my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This pub has very good food.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,About six of us went there.\NWe drank, ate, and had a great time.\NMuch time had passed and it was time to pay the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, Matsumoto-san treated us.\NI thanked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.97,0:00:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,After we left the pub, he said to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.24,0:01:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,"I don't want to tell you because it's your acquaintance's restaurant..."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.94,0:01:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It was only 20,000 yen for six people.\NIt was only 20,000 yen, really good price!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.68,0:01:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But he said,\N"I don't want to say this because it's an acquaintance's restaurant, but that place is a rip-off."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.82,0:01:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cheap, isn't it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.42,0:01:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He kept saying how delicious the food was!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.26,0:01:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The six of us had a great time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.13,0:01:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Only 20,000 yen for 6 people!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.40,0:01:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Only 20,000 yen!\NIt was REALLY REALLY REALLY good price!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.70,0:01:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But he said!!,\N"That place is a rip-off."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.14,0:01:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell!\NI don't need you guys to tell me that!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.01,0:01:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how many times I've treated you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.11,0:01:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We want you to show us how cool you are.\NYou're our leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"Our"!?\NYou have nothing to do with us!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.36,0:01:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- We belong to Yoshimoto, but you belong to Jinrikisha!!\N- No! I'm in Yoshimoto too!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.33,0:01:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is that so!?\N- No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-  I'm in Yoshimoto too!\N- You are not!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.50,0:02:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Pants sold at Uniqlo or Jeansmate are usually around 3,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.28,0:02:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't buy that easily in the fitting room, saying\N"Ummm. I can't make up my mind!  I can't decide!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.42,0:02:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He picked up a camouflage outfit and asked me,\N"What do you think of this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like camouflage pattern, but he is my senior,\Nso I said, "Oh, this is good."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked at the price tag and said,\N"This is nice, I'll buy it."\NIt was 8,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"I can't afford this."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.71,0:02:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He could buy the whole store if he wanted to!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.95,0:02:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!\NThat's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's true!\N- No, that's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck you all!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what the hell are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm standing on the witn...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a big nose and small nostrils!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That has nothing to do with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.34,0:03:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- You should be in The Best 100 Noses in Japan!\N- What the hell is that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.31,0:03:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He will definitely be chosen for The Best 100 Noses in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.75,0:03:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's next, Endo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Not from me.\NThe witnesses are here, may I allow them to enter the court?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- Witnesses, please enter the court.\N- Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.04,0:03:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,For those of you who don't know them, let me introduce them.\NHe's Matsumoto-san's manager, Fujiwara-san.\NAnd he is Hamada-san's manager, Kimoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.98,0:03:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how long have you been his manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,More than three and a half years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:04:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- Three and a half years.\N- Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Most of the time, the manager is with the comedian.\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He had been with the defendant for three and a half years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you had any treats from him in those three and a half years?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lie!\NHe's lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought him a cup of coffee at the L.A. airport!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.99,0:04:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny!!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.03,0:04:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that Fujiwara-san has not said anything suggests that he has never been treated by the defendant otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, Kimoto-san.\NHow long have you been Hamada-san's manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- About three years and four months.\N- About the same as him?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever had a treat from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:05:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He often says to me after work, "I'm tired.\NLet's eat yakiniku together."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakiniku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Choice cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The meat at the yakiniku restaurant he takes him to is not beef.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's beef, right?\N- Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.93,0:05:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hamada-san, is that beef?\N- Definitely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- And what kind of beef did you have?\N- Choice cut beef.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- That was DEFINITELY a choice cut beef.\N- DEFINITELY!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- Of course he has bought you a cup of coffee, hasn't he?\N- Many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.22,0:05:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, he buys it with the money in my wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain later!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's ask him about that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he give you anything for your birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- It was my birthday last month.\N- Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:06:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was alone with him in the dressing room, he took 50,000 yen out of his pocket and gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.61,0:06:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Cool!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.05,0:06:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not something to be applauded!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just doing the obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.96,0:06:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a episode to praise Hamada rather than condemn me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not.\NWhy did you give him 50,000 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know what he wanted, so I figured he could buy whatever he wanted with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He is awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He is cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujiwara, talk about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.72,0:06:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about that quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Did that really happen?\NIf so, please talk about it for Matsumoto-san's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:07:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my birthday, but every year on his birthday, he receives a big cake and a big bouquet of flowers from Gaki's staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- We all ate the cake together.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to give the bouquet to Matsumoto-san on his way home.\NThen he said, "I don't want those, you give them to your wife," so I took them and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a present from him to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.62,0:07:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujiwara, not that!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about what happened the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.36,0:07:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Did that really happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, tell us about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about that,\Nor rather, make something up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fabrication!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Make something up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,“Make” ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't have that kind of skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But Fujiwara-san gave Matsumoto-san a birthday present.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:08:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?\NDid you give him something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he gave me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.66,0:08:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I gave him a necktie pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.70,0:08:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though he gave Matsumoto-san a necktie pin, he did not receive anything from Matsumoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Frankly speaking, I don't need a necktie pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!!\NYou guys get the hell out of here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We're closed!\NGo home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.79,0:08:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me, you're disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- Go away!\N- Sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- What the hell is that?\N- He tickles him.\N- They are classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- Trip to Ise Case -
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a case from a few years ago when Matsumoto, Kimura, Imada, and Itao went to Ise for a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When we got to Ise, let's eat a lot of good food.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!\NIse lobsters are very tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The four had a great time in the car and they arrived at Ise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Parque España!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The four of them enjoyed the sights.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Matsumoto said.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,As I recall, there was a Nichii earlier, wasn't there?\NCan we stop by there before eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He couldn't help but stop by there, as Nichii was very interesting to Matsumoto, who was interested in cheap stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:10:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, This is a nice T-shirt!\NIt's so cheap! I have to buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto was very excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And then his shopping was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.  Let's eat something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.66,0:10:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, I can eat lobster.\NHow dare you waste my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.07,0:10:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't these places have restaurants in the basement?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Contrary to what the three of us thought, Matsumoto headed for an udon restaurant in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.48,0:10:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,When Matsumoto saw the food they ordered, he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.02,0:10:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They sold croquettes over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimu, can you go get me some of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But isn't it bad to bring them in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you ask the waiterabout that, asshole?\NOh well, I'll ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.57,0:11:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, can I bring something in?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, you are not allowed to bring in anything, but the clerk reluctantly agreed to Matsumoto's request.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.55,0:11:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He then added croquettes, which Kimura had bought, to the side dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be gorgeous with this!\NThe size has increased, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.93,0:11:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The three were stunned by Matsumoto's delight at the udon set meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, they had to come all the way to Ise to eat udon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,0:11:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Judge, may I call a witness?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.48,0:11:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Witness, please enter the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.59,0:11:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't look like a comedian!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.93,0:11:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He's looking sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true what happened at the VCR?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I thought I wouldn't tell this story until I die if I didn't have this opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.84,0:12:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- I see.\N- This is a good opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.41,0:12:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing is bothering me.\NYou guys were planning to eat lobsters and other seafood, but ended up eating udon noodles, was that lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That was not lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.19,0:12:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That was dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.86,0:12:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that lunch!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No. If it was lunch, I would have udon and enjoy dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- Was that dinner!?\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That was UNTHINKABLE.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to wait in the car while he was shopping at Nichii.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.\NWhen he's done shopping, you guys can go to the restaurant right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.85,0:12:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But he wanted to see the grocery section in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where he found Tacchan Croquettes.\NFor some reason, he took an unusual interest in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? He had eaten them before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ise one might taste different, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He was so interested in it that I thought Umemiya-san might have his weakness.\N"Oh, they sell them in these places too!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I can see why he was interested in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a bit of a confession, but I figured if he ate a couple of them, his stomach would growl a little, and we could have lobster or abalone an hour or so later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a mom's idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! I think it's stingy to think like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I think is a stingy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why are you\Nlooking at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Snap out of it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:14:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You came to Ise for a luxurious meal, and you're fine with udon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He usually eats luxurious meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.56,0:14:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.29,0:14:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.23,0:14:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"Nope"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.50,0:14:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I also don't understand why he was so incredibly excited at Parque España.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How was he excited?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.14,0:14:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Four of us got on a boat and went on an attraction where we drifted down a river.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,At the end, the river splits in two and It goes down about 3 meters and goes outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought "hmmm", but he was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a funny guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He comes up with more funny stuff, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- What the hell.\N- I have something I want to apologize to Yamazaki, Cocorico, and Ameagari for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys interacted with him later than I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I didn't stop his stinginess when I met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's okay!\N- Please don't apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.21,0:15:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!!\NI'll tell you one thing!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.18,0:15:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no fun being\Nwith you guys!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no fun playing\Nwith you guys!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why did you say\N"When I trip, all I need is for Kimu to be there" to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just being polite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out!!\NYou're all a bunch of pussies!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:16:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There is so much more I want to say, but I can't seem to say it in words, so I wrote him a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, please read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,When you went to Russia the other day, I got a 40 yen pin badge as a souvenir from you for the first time.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.09,0:16:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Prices are low in Russia!\NEven if that is 40 yen in Japan, it might be worth 40,000 yen in Russia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is true!\N"You're full of it"?\NWho the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your hood up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't see anything for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Kimura-kun, read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you knou it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,by Yuichi Kimura
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.28,0:16:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- Was that the title?\N- Do you know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.39,0:16:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I always carry 9 yen with me for you, because you hate saving coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.56,0:16:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though the video you rented was quite overdue, I paid the late fee and return the video on your behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.14,0:17:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,At last year's year-end party, you gave me 10,000 yen short of the amount I wanted you to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,At a karaoke party with about 10 people, you said, "I'll leave first, I'll give you this much," and the money you gave me was only enough for three people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,People say that high income earners who frequent Don Quijote and 100-yen stores are stingy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.68,0:17:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How unpleasant!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How unpleasant!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.68,0:17:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,After this, testimonies from his friends revealed an unbelievable fact about Matsumoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:17:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The trial then reaches its climax.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Judge, may I play the next VCR?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.93,0:18:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is a special testimonial VCR that was received from his associates.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is 130R's Itao-san's wedding celebration case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.38,0:18:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to celebrate Itao-san's wedding in a big way, so I decided to make the congratulatory gift 100,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I put 100,000 yen in an envelope and arrived at the venue.\NAnd I was curious about one thing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Ochoko-Matsumoto did something stingy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.34,0:18:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked the staff how much Matsumoto-san gave him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.18,0:18:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I got the sad information that it was a 70,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:19:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to congratulate Itao-san, but I took 50,000 yen out of 100,000 yen and changed 50,000 yen to the congratulatory money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you should give him 200,000 or 300,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Show us a little more of what you pay for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We played a team game in jerseys with him in Gottsu-e-kanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted the jersey he wore for the shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a jersey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Since that time you were making a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But why did you take that jersey home?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.96,0:19:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I honestly thought you were pathetic like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, please treat me to something just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He has taken care of me for 15 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The first treat he gave me was 170 yen udon noodles from the basement of a department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be wondering what I am talking about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.76,0:20:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I think back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,For fifteen years I have been.....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,For fifteen years...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,For fifteen years...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I often go out with him by car.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason, Matsumoto-san always says, "Let's go in one car."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:21:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It is because there are five of us and it is more fun to all ride together in one car than to split into two or three and trip separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.77,0:21:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.88,0:21:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So we try to take one car whenever we go somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But one day it occurred to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.69,0:21:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes we go in Matsumoto-san's car, and sometimes we go in my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.23,0:21:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"Huh?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.87,0:21:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"He uses my car only when we goes to far places."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.71,0:21:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.38,0:21:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The gas money?\NHe cares about gas money?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.08,0:21:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No one does that!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.85,0:21:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm just imagining things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.05,0:21:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No one does that!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it for the VCR testimonials.\NWhat did you all think about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.70,0:22:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The last one about gas money was an eye opener.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been pissed off for a while now, why is Onuma there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.41,0:22:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy has nothing to do with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.18,0:22:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And his suit is most autumnal!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.82,0:22:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been watching you the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been watching you the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.42,0:22:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the instigator of this trial.\NThat can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.16,0:22:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Judge, please give your verdict.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.30,0:22:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I will now pronounce the verdict.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.57,0:22:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I will now pronounce the verdict.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.64,0:22:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an undeniable fact that the defendant, Matsumoto Hitoshi, has caused trouble for many people in spite of being so rich,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And it far exceeded our eg...expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.72,0:22:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It can’t be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.62,0:23:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, we consider it indefensible and the sentence is guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.66,0:23:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We sentence him to the "Let's withdraw 1 million yen from his savings and splurge!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.41,0:23:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.18,0:23:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make sense, right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.01,0:23:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make any sense!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.35,0:23:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.95,0:23:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.55,0:23:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a Japanese TV show!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.75,0:23:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time we'll do your "Too Stupid Trial".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.39,0:23:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.22,0:23:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.46,0:23:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.86,0:23:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.63,0:23:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And next week,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.70,0:23:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We will broadcast the execution of "Let's withdraw 1 million yen from stingy Matsumoto's savings and splurge!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.57,0:23:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaki no Tsukai's original video"Flame Talk: Legend of the 20th Century Part 2", now on sale!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.85,0:24:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,100 winners will be selected by drawing from among those who have purchased it, and will receive a picture book of\N"The Best Selection of Stingy Onuma's Trial".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.72,0:24:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[Subbed by RAIDEN1017]
